<paragraph id="8BD390772C7EF4529306FED6F342FE3C" blockId="15.[831,1336,371,398]" box="[831,1336,371,398]" pageId="15" pageNumber="118">
<heading id="D09B271B2C7EF4529306FED6F342FE3C" box="[831,1336,371,398]" centered="true" fontSize="12" level="2" pageId="15" pageNumber="118" reason="2">
<taxonomicName id="4C6CEBF42C7EF4529306FED6F342FE3C" authority="PACE, 2001" authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="2001" box="[831,1336,371,398]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Leptusa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="118" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="jinfomontis" subGenus="Drepanoleptusa">
<emphasis id="B9184C652C7EF4529306FED6F5EAFE3C" box="[831,912,371,398]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="118">Leptusa</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="B9184C652C7EF45293A7FED6F23BFE3C" box="[926,1089,371,398]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="118">Drepanoleptusa</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis id="B9184C652C7EF4529477FED6F2BAFE3C" box="[1102,1216,371,398]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="118">jinfomontis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFFDED862C7EF45294FEFED6F342FE3C" author="PACE, R." box="[1223,1336,371,398]" pageId="15" pageNumber="118" pagination="151 - 160" refId="ref18520" refString="PACE, R. 2001: Nuove specie cinesi del genere Leptusa. Monografia del genere Leptusa KRAATZ: Supplemento XII (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae). - Bollettino del Museo Regionale di Scienze Naturali, Torino 18: 151 - 160." type="journal article" year="2001">PACE, 2001</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BD390772C7EF4529323FE0CF22FFDF3" blockId="15.[794,1399,425,577]" pageId="15" pageNumber="118">
This species was originally assigned to the subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="4C6CEBF42C7EF4529323FE6CF263FE53" authority="PACE, 1992" authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="1992" box="[794,1049,457,481]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Nesopisalia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="118" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9184C652C7EF4529323FE6CF5EAFE53" box="[794,912,457,481]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="118">Nesopisalia</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFFDED862C7EF45293A4FE6CF263FE53" author="PACE, R." box="[925,1049,457,481]" pageId="15" pageNumber="118" pagination="111 - 119" refId="ref18312" refString="PACE, R. 1992: Il genere Leptusa KRAATZ della sottoregione indocinese (Taiwan e Vietnam). Monografia del genere Leptusa Kraatz: Supplemento I (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae). - Elytron 5 [1991]: 111 - 119." type="journal article" year="1992">PACE, 1992</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFFDED862C7EF4529416FE6CF2D0FE53" author="PACE, R." box="[1071,1194,457,481]" pageId="15" pageNumber="118" pagination="111 - 119" refId="ref18312" refString="PACE, R. 1992: Il genere Leptusa KRAATZ della sottoregione indocinese (Taiwan e Vietnam). Monografia del genere Leptusa Kraatz: Supplemento I (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae). - Elytron 5 [1991]: 111 - 119." type="journal article" year="1992">PACE 1992</bibRefCitation>
). The illustrations provided by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFFDED862C7EF4529399FE4CF259FDB3" author="PACE, R." box="[928,1059,489,513]" pageId="15" pageNumber="118" pagination="151 - 160" refId="ref18520" refString="PACE, R. 2001: Nuove specie cinesi del genere Leptusa. Monografia del genere Leptusa KRAATZ: Supplemento XII (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae). - Bollettino del Museo Regionale di Scienze Naturali, Torino 18: 151 - 160." type="journal article" year="2001">PACE (2001)</bibRefCitation>
suggest, however, that it is very closely related to 
<taxonomicName id="4C6CEBF42C7EF45293F6FDAFF243FD93" authorityName="ASSING" authorityYear="2006" box="[975,1081,521,545]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Leptusa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="118" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="discolor">
<emphasis id="B9184C652C7EF45293F6FDAFF243FD93" box="[975,1081,521,545]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="118">L. discolor</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C6CEBF42C7EF4529455FDAFF2A5FD93" authorityName="Assing" authorityYear="2021" box="[1132,1247,522,545]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Leptusa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="118" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="emeiana">
<emphasis id="B9184C652C7EF4529455FDAFF2A5FD93" box="[1132,1247,522,545]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="118">L. emeiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(see below) of the subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="4C6CEBF42C7EF4529393FD8CF235FDF3" authorityName="PACE" authorityYear="1982" box="[938,1103,553,577]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Leptusa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="15" pageNumber="118" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Drepanoleptusa">
<emphasis id="B9184C652C7EF4529393FD8CF235FDF3" box="[938,1103,553,577]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="118">Drepanoleptusa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
